            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Sony 早前推出全新頭戴式無線降噪耳機 ULT WEAR，ULT WEAR 屬次旗艦級別耳機，在耳機位置加入了 ULT 按鍵，可供用家切換兩種重低音模式。ULT WEAR 有齊音色、主動降噪、3D 頭部追蹤音效、DSEE 數碼音質升技術等旗艦耳機擁有的功能，而定價只有旗艦耳機約一半，絕對抵玩！事不宜遲，即刻開箱評測。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243117 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09378-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09378-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09378-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>黑白</strong><strong>灰三</strong><strong>色</strong><strong> 低調設計不易留痕</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ULT WEAR 的設計及外觀頗為簡潔，耳機側面印有細小雷射反光的 Sony 字樣，低調設計同時不乏個性。機身用上了磨砂質地，摸上手舒適，不易留下指紋等污漬。ULT WEAR 有 3 款顏色選擇，小編拿到的是黑色，型格之選。另外還有灰白色和森林灰色，感覺比較優雅高貴，更會適合女士。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243118 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09439-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09439-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09439-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ULT WEAR 的設計及外觀簡潔，機身用上了磨砂質地，摸上手舒適，不易留下指紋等污漬</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243119 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09377-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09377-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09377-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳機側面印有細小雷射反光的 Sony 字樣</p><h2><strong>耳罩不重</strong> <strong>佩戴感舒適</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ULT WEAR 包裝附送了 1 個收納袋，裏面有 1 條 USB-C 充電線及 1 條 3.5mm 線。ULT WEAR 是頭罩式耳機，機身只重 255 克，小編戴了 2 小時感覺實淨，耳罩用料記憶綿，亦不會輕易掉下，耳罩尺寸剛好，未有太大侷促感。但如要將耳機掛頸，感覺就有點不舒服，不太適合長時間掛頸。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243122 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09385-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09385-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09385-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ULT WEAR 包裝附送了 1 個收納袋</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243123 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09387-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09387-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09387-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲裏面有 1 條 USB-C 充電線及 1 條 3.5mm 線</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243121 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09427-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09427-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09427-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳罩尺寸剛好，未有太大侷促感</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243124 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09433-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09433-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09433-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲但如要將耳機掛頸，感覺就有點不舒服</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/24/sony-xperia-1-vi-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相機　功能　效能開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/15/sony-xperia-1-vi-first-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相機　介面快速評測 + 開賣詳情公佈</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/08/50-percent-of-sonys-active-userbase-is-still-on-ps4/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">近半 PS 活躍玩家仍在玩 PS4　Sony：「仍然是事業的重要部分」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2><strong>保留</strong><strong>實體鍵</strong> <strong>「</strong><strong>ULT</strong><strong>」增強低音</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ULT WEAR 保留了一部份實體鍵，而未有採用完全輕觸式設計，還原實體鍵的直接感，可減少誤觸的風險。所有實體鍵集中在左耳罩，操控方面頗為簡單，最底在 USB-C 充電口旁的按鍵是開關掣，可用作藍牙配對或開關。旁邊有切換主動降噪及環境聲按鍵。值得一提，ULT WEAR 新增了一個「ULT」按鍵，可供用家切換重低音模式及重低音增強模式，切換時耳機會發出提示聲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243126 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09384-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09384-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09384-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最底在 USB-C 充電口旁的按鍵是開關掣，可用作藍牙配對或開關，旁邊有切換主動降噪及環境聲按鍵</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243125 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09424-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09424-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09424-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ULT WEAR 新增了一個「ULT」按鍵，可供用家切換重低音模式及重低音增強模式，切換時耳機會發出提示聲</p><h2><strong>Sony Headphones</strong> <strong>自定義</strong> <strong>EQ</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Sony 向來都有自家應用程式，用家可以下載 Headphones ，調整主動降噪、通透模式、EQ 等。EQ 方面就預設 10 項，分別是「歡快」、「激昂」、「醇美」、「放鬆」、「聲樂」、「強化高音」、「強化重音」、「演説」、「手動」及 2 項自訂。用家亦可按下設定圖示，選擇「ULT 1」、「ULT 2」或「ULT OFF」開啟或關閉重低音及重低音增強，同時可選擇增強的程度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243129 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243130 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-1-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-1-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-1-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家可以下載 Headphones ，調整主動降噪、通透模式、EQ 等</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243131 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-2-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-2-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-2-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲EQ 方面就預設 10 項，分別是「歡快」、「激昂」、「醇美」等，及 2 項自訂</p><h2><strong>多裝置連接，非常方便實用</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ULT WEAR 有多裝置連接，用家可同時連上電腦及手機，小編工作時經常不止用一個裝置，所以覺得這功能非常實用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243132 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09434-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09434-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09434-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可多裝置連接</p><h2>通透模式有驚喜</h2><p>ULT WEAR 使用了降風噪結構，耳機內外都具備雙噪音感應器，加上 V1 整合處理器，可以有效捕捉及隔絕環境聲。小編特別欣賞其環境聲，清晰之餘亦相對自然，不似其他耳機仍有一定的侷促感，ULT WEAR 收音也未見刻意放大。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243133 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09379-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09379-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09379-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小編特別欣賞其環境聲，清晰之餘亦相對自然</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/24/sony-xperia-1-vi-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相機　功能　效能開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/15/sony-xperia-1-vi-first-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相機　介面快速評測 + 開賣詳情公佈</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/08/50-percent-of-sonys-active-userbase-is-still-on-ps4/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">近半 PS 活躍玩家仍在玩 PS4　Sony：「仍然是事業的重要部分」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2><strong>支援快速充電，充電</strong> <strong>3 分鐘可用 90 </strong><strong>分鐘</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">續航力方面，充滿電的 ULT WEAR 最多可以連續使用 50 小時，超長的使用時間足夠小編用 4 至 5 日。ULT WEAR 支援快速充電，只要充電 3 分鐘，即可使用 90 分鐘，充電 10 分鐘更可使用 5 小時，可謂是驚人。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243135 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan094232-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan094232-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan094232-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ULT WEAR 支援快速充電，只要充電 3 分鐘，即可使用 90 分鐘</p><h2><strong>音場闊，適合強調低音的流行曲</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ULT WEAR 可使用 LDAC 制式，加上使用了 40mm 動圈單元，加強了耳機的低頻處理。小編在 Sony XPERIA 上使用 MOOV 播放 Mr. 的《黑色狂迷》，歌曲屬於搖滾樂，編曲比較複雜但 ULT WEAR 在低頻上更提升一個層次，「UTL」功能提供了足夠份量及下潛力，惟分析力中等，在處理編曲複雜的歌曲未太稱心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243136 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Mr.《黑色狂迷》</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">謝安琪的《十二月二十二》錄音版本。明顯聽到音場闊、聽到歌曲細節。惟歌曲將人聲靠前，高頻及人聲聲音突出，與 ULT WEAR 耳機特點相違背，不太強調人聲及高頻，用家需透過調較 EQ 方可獲得更清澈的高頻人聲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243137 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-1-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-1-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-1-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲謝安琪《十二月二十二》</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">再聽聽黃耀明的《身外情》，歌曲開頭已有低沉的低音結他，ULT WEAR 都展現出處理低頻的能力，低音結他的下潛力強勁，是刻意強調低音，卻不致於失去平衡，反而昇華了歌曲本身的特色。高頻音色方面未是 ULT WEAR 的強項，但亦恰到好處。整體來説，ULT WEAR 音場闊，適合收聽強調低音的流行曲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243138 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-2-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-2-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406141-2-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲黃耀明《身外情》</p><h2>兩種重低音效果比較</h2><p>以 Mr.《黑色狂迷》為例，搖滾樂開啟重低音模式的確比關閉更適合，重低音加強了歌曲的節奏感，但小編認為「UTL 1」已足夠，使用「UTL 2」反而會使有點低頻過於用力，失去了應有平衡。用家亦可在 Headphones 等化器中微調重低音的份量。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243167 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-3-694x416.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="416" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-3-694x416.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot_202406131-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家亦可在 Headphones 等化器中微調重低音的份量</p><h2><strong>總結：</strong><strong>低頻強勁</strong> <strong>續航力夠</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ULT WEAR 的售價為 HK$ 1599，屬中價位，在功能上都拍得住旗艦耳機，又有強勁低頻音色，再加上續航力達 50 小時。價錢只需一半旗艦耳機的約一半，性價比極高，適合喜歡聽低頻的使用者。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/24/sony-xperia-1-vi-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相機　功能　效能開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/15/sony-xperia-1-vi-first-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相機　介面快速評測 + 開賣詳情公佈</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/08/50-percent-of-sonys-active-userbase-is-still-on-ps4/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">近半 PS 活躍玩家仍在玩 PS4　Sony：「仍然是事業的重要部分」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/sony-ult-wear-wh-ult900n/mobile-music/headphones/">【評測】Sony ULT WEAR WH-ULT900N 真無線重低音頭戴耳機，兩種重低音模式比較 + 性價比高 + 續航力高</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
